---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | Lovely Jubbly Removals"
  description="Privacy policy for lovelyjubblyremovals.co.uk. Learn how we collect, use, and protect your personal information."
  canonical="/privacy-policy/"
  slug="privacy-policy"
  breadcrumbName="Privacy Policy"
>
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">Last updated: January 2026</p>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <h2>Introduction</h2>
        <p>
          This website (lovelyjubblyremovals.co.uk) is operated by Soborbo Ltd. This privacy policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you use our website.
        </p>
        <p>
          Lovely Jubbly Removals ceased trading in 2023. This website now serves to direct enquiries to Painless Removals, who provide removal services in the Bristol area.
        </p>

        <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>When you submit a callback request form, we collect:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Your name</li>
          <li>Your phone number</li>
          <li>Your email address (if provided)</li>
          <li>Your preferred callback time</li>
          <li>Any message you include</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>We use your information to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Forward your enquiry to Painless Removals so they can contact you about removal services</li>
          <li>Respond to your questions or requests</li>
          <li>Improve our website and services</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Information Sharing</h2>
        <p>
          When you submit a callback request, your details are shared with Painless Removals (operated by Soborbo Ltd) so they can respond to your enquiry. We do not sell or share your information with any other third parties for marketing purposes.
        </p>

        <h2>Data Retention</h2>
        <p>
          We retain your enquiry data for up to 2 years to help us handle any follow-up questions. After this period, your data is securely deleted.
        </p>

        <h2>Your Rights</h2>
        <p>Under GDPR, you have the right to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Access the personal data we hold about you</li>
          <li>Request correction of inaccurate data</li>
          <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
          <li>Object to processing of your data</li>
          <li>Request data portability</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          To exercise any of these rights, please contact us at hello@painlessremovals.com.
        </p>

        <h2>Cookies</h2>
        <p>
          This website uses essential cookies to ensure basic functionality. We do not use tracking or advertising cookies.
        </p>

        <h2>Contact Us</h2>
        <p>
          If you have any questions about this privacy policy or how we handle your data, please contact:
        </p>
        <p>
          Soborbo Ltd<br />
          Email: hello@painlessremovals.com<br />
          Phone: 01172 870 082<br />
          Address: 290-294 Southmead Rd, Bristol BS10 5EN
        </p>

        <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>
          We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated revision date.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
